{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazztja tas KUNGS mehs zaur juhfo Rohbeschahm\nus Mohsu un us Aäronu/ tadeht effaun isgahjufchi.\nka juhs man ne effat tizzejufchi /\nka juhs man buhtut fwehtijuschi\npreekſch Israëta Behrnu Azziin/\ntad juhs ne eerweddifeet scho\nDraudsi us to Semmi / ko es\nwinneem dewis efmu."
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Schis irr tas Bahrscha-\nnas-Uhdens / kadeht tee Israëta\nBehrni ar to KUNGII bahrahs/\nun wiꞥſch tappe pee teem fweh-\ntihts."
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fuhtija Mohsus Wel-\nstis no Kahdefa / pee to Eedoma\nRehniru / (tee fazzija): Ta fal-\nka taws Brahlis Israëls; Tu sin-\nni wiﬀas tahs Behdas / kas\nmums irr usgahjufschas."
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ka muhtu Tehwi usEgip-\ntes-Semmi irr nogahjufschi / un\nka mehs Egiptes-Semmê ilgu\nPaiku effam dshwojufschi / un ka\ntee Egipteri mums / un muhfeem\nTehweem irr faundarrjufschi."
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad brehzain mehs us to\nKUNGU / un wiꞥſch klauttja\nmuhsu Balksni/ un fuhtija we-\nnu Engeli un iswedde muhs no\nEgiptes - Semmes / un redsi/\nmehs effim Kahdefâ/ weenâ Pils-\nsahta us juhsu pehdigahm Roh-\nbeschahm."
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Laid mehs zaur faruu\nSemmi eetam / mehs ne eetim\npahr Druwehm/ zaur Wihna-\nDahrseem/ ueds dsersim Uhdent\nno Akkahm / pa Leel-Zeltu eefim\nmehs/ueds greesifimees pa labbas\nueds pa kreifas Rohkas/ teekans"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet Eedoms fazztja us to:\nTew ne buhs zaur mann eet / zit-\ntadt es iseeſchu tew ar Sobbinu\npretti."
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazztja tee Israëta\nBehrni / pa staigatu Zeltu eefim\nmehs / un ja mehs no tawa Uh-\ndens Dserkim / mehs ar fatweem\nLohpeem/ tad dohtim mehs Mak-\nfu par to / mehs ne gribbam zitta\nne ka/ ka Rahjahm zaureet."
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch fazzija : Tew ne\nbuhs zaureet/ un Eedoms isgahje\nwinnam pretti ar warreneem\nZaudim/un stipru Rohku."
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta aisleedse Eedoms Isra-\netam/ ne taudams winnu zaur fa-\nwahm Rohbeschahm eet / ta at-\nstahe Israëts no winna."
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad afgahje tee no Kah-\ndefa / un wiﬀa Israëta Behrni\nDraudse nahze pee to Kalnu Or."
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad runnaja tas KUNGS\nus Mohsu / un us Aäronu pee ta\nKalna Or / pee tahs Eedoma\nSemnes Rohbeschahm / fazzji\ndans:"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Airoxam buhs fatweem\nLandim peeliktam tapt/ jo wiꞥſch\nne nahks eeſsch to Semmi/ ko es-\nteem Israëta Behrneem dewie\nesnuu / tapehz ka juhs mannam\nWahrdam effat prettiturreju-\nscheeg / pee ta Bahrschanas- Uh-\ndens."
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Neimm Astronu/ un wiꞥſch\nna Dehtu Eeleasaru / un laid te\nkahpj augfcham us to Kalnu Or"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
